text: Diana Khisa (born 26 May 1987) is a Kenyan volleyball player. She is part of the Kenyan women's national volleyball team. She competed at the 2007 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup, 2011 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup, 2011 FIVB Women's Club World Championship, 2012 FIVB Women's Club World Championship, 2013 FIVB Women's Club World Championship, and 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Kenya Pipeline Company and Kenya Prisons. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan volleyball players
